trans-unit.source: Generates the HTML markup that is used to render the associated <xref href="System.Web.DynamicData.DynamicDataManager"></xref> control at design time.

trans-unit.source: The GetDesignTimeHtml method calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.CreatePlaceHolderDesignTimeHtml%2A> method to generate a simple rectangular placeholder representation that displays the type and ID of the control.
trans-unit.target: GetDesignTimeHtml メソッドの呼び出し、<xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.CreatePlaceHolderDesignTimeHtml%2A>型とコントロールの ID を表示する単純な四角形のプレース ホルダーの表示を生成する方法</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.CreatePlaceHolderDesignTimeHtml%2A>。
